# yaml-language-server: $schema=../templates.schema.json
# source_id: 3092
# teaser: Supercharge your content production! Generate very detailed content outlines for your human
# writers. Includes FAQs and attention-grabbing headings.
- id: 3092-better-content-outlines-2-0
  title: Better content outlines 2.0
  tags:
  - writing
  - better
  - content
  - outlines
  family: writing
  body: 'Create long-form content outline in markdown [TARGETLANGUAGE]. The content
    outline should include a minimum of 20 headings and subheadings. The outline should
    be extensive and cover the whole topic. Use fully detailed subheadings that engage
    the reader. The outline should also have a conclusion followed by a list of FAQs
    relevant to the topic. Please provide a catchy title for the article. Don''t write
    the article, only the outline for writers. The topic of the article is: "[PROMPT]".'
  enabled: true
  required:
  - prompt
  - targetlanguage
